@page "/"

<PageTitle>AI Chat</PageTitle>

<div class="home-page">

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-eyebrow">
            <span class="hero-badge">
                <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 8v4l2 2"/></svg>
                Powered by Azure AI Foundry
            </span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="hero-title">Your AI workspace,<br /><span class="hero-accent">built for real work.</span></h1>
        <p class="hero-sub">
            Chat with multiple Azure OpenAI deployments, upload documents for grounded answers, and keep your
            conversation history secure with Azure Entra ID, Key Vault encryption, and SQL-backed storage.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-cta">
            <a class="cta-primary" href="/chat">
                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M22 2L11 13"/><path d="M22 2L15 22L11 13L2 9L22 2Z"/></svg>
                Start chatting
            </a>
            <a class="cta-secondary" href="/chat">New conversation</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="stats-row">
        <div class="stat-item">
            <span class="stat-number">∞</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Deployments supported</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-divider"></div>
        <div class="stat-item">
            <span class="stat-number">∞</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Conversation history</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-divider"></div>
        <div class="stat-item">
            <span class="stat-number">10+</span>
            <span class="stat-label">File types for RAG</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-divider"></div>
        <div class="stat-item">
            <span class="stat-number">🔒</span>
            <span class="stat-label">AES-256-GCM at rest</span>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="features">
        <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">
                <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 01-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Multi-deployment chat</h3>
            <p>Select any configured Azure AI Foundry deployment per conversation. Responses stream token-by-token and are labelled with the deployment that produced them.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">
                <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v16a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Document grounding (RAG)</h3>
            <p>Attach PDFs, Word docs, spreadsheets, images, and more. Relevant chunks are automatically injected into the prompt so the assistant answers from your content.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">
                <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0110 0v4"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Enterprise security</h3>
            <p>Sign in with Microsoft Entra ID — no local accounts. Conversation data is stored in SQL Server with field-level AES-256-GCM encryption, keys managed by Azure Key Vault.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">
                <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><polyline points="1 4 1 10 7 10"/><path d="M3.51 15a9 9 0 101.85-4.6"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Edit, regenerate &amp; iterate</h3>
            <p>Edit any past message to branch the conversation, or regenerate the last response with the same or a different deployment — without losing your history.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">
                <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><path d="M15 3h4a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-4"/><polyline points="10 17 15 12 10 7"/><line x1="15" y1="12" x2="3" y2="12"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Image &amp; multimodal input</h3>
            <p>Paste or upload images directly into the chat. The assistant processes them alongside your text for fully multimodal conversations.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">
                <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><path d="M19.07 4.93a10 10 0 010 14.14M4.93 4.93a10 10 0 000 14.14"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Streaming responses</h3>
            <p>Assistant replies arrive token-by-token with live Markdown rendering — no waiting for the full response before you start reading.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-banner">
        <div class="cta-banner-inner">
            <div class="cta-banner-text">
                <h2>Ready to get started?</h2>
                <p>Open a conversation and ask anything — or upload a document to ground your answers.</p>
            </div>
            <a class="cta-primary" href="/chat">
                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M22 2L11 13"/><path d="M22 2L15 22L11 13L2 9L22 2Z"/></svg>
                Open chat
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>

</div>
